 &lt;a href="#android" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ya, Android memanglah populer dikalangan pengguna smartphone, &lt;a href="https://gs.statcounter.com/os-market-share/mobile/worldwide" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;data&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; menunjukan bahwa Android menduduki peringkat pertama pengguna smartphone terbanyak di Dunia. Android merupakan sistem operasi sumber terbuka yang dikembangkan oleh &lt;a href="https://www.android.com/" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Google&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; dan &lt;a href="https://www.openhandsetalliance.com/android_overview.html" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Open Handset Alliance&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Android dirancang untuk perangkat ponsel pintar dan tablet.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Bspwm Dotfiles</title><link>https://adilhyz.github.io/projects/adilhyz/dotfiles-v1/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Aug 2023 20:51:11 +0700</pubDate><author>sandyadilhayyi@gmail.com (Adilhyz)</author><guid>https://adilhyz.github.io/projects/adilhyz/dotfiles-v1/</guid><category domain="https://adilhyz.github.io/categories/os/">OS</category><description>&lt;div class="details admonition success open"&gt;
